/*
 * The basic Gawin file
 *
 * When compiled and executed will print 'Hello Gawin!' to stdout
 *
 * Program is initialized using the Gawin Runtime (GRT) and the Gawin Standard Library (gstdlib/gstd)
 * Program is linked at compile-time with all built-in libraries (grtio, grtmem, grtstr)
 *
 * This compilation pipeline is deprecated
 * Linking will include grtio (grthelpio) and grtstr (grthelpstr), but not grtmem
 */

